fields.isi: My name is achmad irfan afandi, I have a strong passion in numbers, mathematics, and formula. My journey as data analyst and data scientist began when my boss often gave me assignments to analyze problems that often occur on machines using Microsoft Excel, until finally I found a new passion when I managed to process data, create formulas, create charts and provide insight and successfully solve problems. And by joining refocus, I can learn and maximizing my passion in data.

fields.title: Refocus Data Analyst Project Food Story
fields.background: This project is to help food story , a cloud kitchen industry to make dashboard for developing their business.
fields.jobdesk1: Provide recommendations to improve their business
fields.jobdesk2: Analyze the condition business of foodstory by making a dashboard microsoft power BI
fields.jobdesk4: Successfully make a profesional interactive dashboard for improve the business of food story and give some recommendations.

fields.title: Refocus Data Analyst Project NHTSA
fields.background: help the National Highway Traffic Safety Administration (NHTSA), NHTSA is one of the government departments government department in the United States that focuses on reducing the number of traffic accidents on highways. NHTSA is currently working on new regulations that will be implemented next year.
fields.jobdesk1: Search the new finding in the data that related with the traffic accident in USA states
fields.jobdesk2: Analyze the current condition of traffic accident based on NHTSA 2020 data in USA using SQL and google spreadsheet
